edu.cs505.finalproject.group4.patterns.factory.weatherfactory - package edu.cs505.finalproject.group4.patterns.factory.weatherfactory
This package contains the implementation of Abstract Factory pattern with WeatherServiceFactory, WeatherService as interfaces and OpenWebMapsWeatherService , WeatherServiceCreatorFactory as classes.
edu.cs505.finalproject.group4.patterns.innerclass.weatheriterator - package edu.cs505.finalproject.group4.patterns.innerclass.weatheriterator
This package contains the implementation of inner class.
edu.cs505.finalproject.group4.patterns.singleton.httpconnectionsingleton - package edu.cs505.finalproject.group4.patterns.singleton.httpconnectionsingleton
This package contains the implementation of Singleton pattern with static member as instance which contains the instance of the Singleton class, private constructor HTTPConnectionRegistry which prevent anybody to instantiate the Singleton class and a static public method getInstance() which provides the global point of access to the Singleton object and returns the instance to the client calling class.
